    "Section 6 displays the conclusion of the study, its limitations, and recommends some studies for future research.",
    "There are various overlapping definitions of virtual learning in the literature, as well as inconsistencies.",
    "Singh and Thurman (2019), for example, assume that technological advancements coincided with the rise and development of virtual learning, and to minimize overlapping, they argue that virtual learning should constitute the type of technological and digital platforms utilized in the learning process.",
